Sure. For example, in:

https://www.metafor-project.org/doku.php/tips:model_selection_with_glmulti_and_mumin

using

V <- diag(dat$vi)

rma.glmulti <- function(formula, data, ...)
   rma.mv(formula, V, random = ~ 1 | id, data=data, method="ML", ...)

also works just fine.

Best,
Wolfgang

